## Write a program to find perimeter of a rectangle

Perimeter of rectangle = 2 × (`Length` + `Width`)

```
Length : 2
Width  : 3

Perimeter : 10
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="find-perimeter-of-a-rectangle" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){
    int len,breadth;
    scanf("%d",&len);
    scanf("%d",&breadth);
    printf("%d\n",2*(len+breadth));
    return 0;
}

//Contributed by Raghav Garg
